734286f-a.title: Harlem River - Manhattan - Sherman Creek - 10th Avenue - Marginal Street.
734286f-a.text:
(1) Harlem River, Sherman's Creek (a tributary of the Harlem River) east from Tenth Ave. (left) to Marginal Street, showing its north shore as viewed from Dyckman Street.
October 27, 1927
P.L. Sperr

(2) The same, to a point slightly westward (left).
October 27, 1927
P.L. Sperr
